 with mid-size multi-channel retail brands.<\/b><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>It serves as an operational hub to brand operations, centralizing inventory across all sales channels and locations for better control and visibility.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3>4. Khaos Control<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Khaos Control is a cloud-based order management solution from the UK that has been around for 20 years.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>While their rates start at \u00a363 per user, per month, they also offer a free trial.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Khaos Control\u2019s most notable features include:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Multichannel selling software online and in-store<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Integrated accounts and custom reporting<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Advanced stock control and warehouse management<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image size-full wp-image-5540\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.digitalsilk.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/magento-order-management-system-khaoscontrol.jpg\" alt=\"khaos control home page\" class=\"wp-image-5540\"\/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">[Source: <a href=\"https:\/\/www.khaoscontrol.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Khaos Control<\/a>]<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<h3>5. Brightpearl<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Last on our list is Brightpearl, a cloud-based order management system that can manage your eCommerce store\u2019s accounting, CRM, order and inventory management.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Brightpearl\u2019s pricing is quote-based, but they highlight that they primarily base their rates on order volume.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image size-full wp-image-5541\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.digitalsilk.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/magento-order-management-system-brightpearl.jpg\" alt=\"brightpearl home page\" class=\"wp-image-5541\"\/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">[Source: <a href=\"https:\/\/www.brightpearl.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Brightpear<\/a>l]<\/figcapt