 marketing systems to unify your data flow, provide real-time analytics, and improve inventory management, productivity and client satisfaction.<\/span><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3><span data-contrast=\"none\">Step 4: Security<\/span><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p><span data-contrast=\"none\">Our experts closely monitor Magento\u2019s regular security updates so we can upgrade your solution and keep your customer data safe.<\/span><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Step 5: Functional QA<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>We then test your integrations in the staging environment (sandbox).<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Once your eCommerce store is up and running, we start conducting tests in your production environment to make sure everything is running seamlessly.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Step 6: Launch<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Once the QA is complete, your e-store is ready for take-off!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Step 7: Support And Maintenance<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Our services don\u2019t end even after your e-store has been launched.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>After each successful launch, we offer additional support and maintenance services to ensure your e-store is flexible, secure and performs according to the latest industry and technology trends so you stay competitive and a step ahead of your competition.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Digital-Silks-Additional-Magento-Services\"><\/span>Digital Silk&#8217;s Additional Magento Services<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Integration of your order management system isn\u2019t the only Magento service we offer.<b> Our certified Magento developers can help you with any Magento project, including:<\/b><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Magento End-to-End Development Services<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>We equip your\u202fMagento\u202fe-store with the latest features and functionalities in online shopping:\u202fresponsive design, high speed, flexibility, security and more.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Our\u202fexperts build custom\u202fshopping experiences<\/strong>\u202fcentered\u202fon\u202fyour target customers to\u202fincre